          <p>The save DC for the <a href="ch61s02.html#MonstersB-C16">abyssal greater basilisk's</a> petrifying gaze (DC 21) is adjusted for its greater Hit Dice and higher Charisma score.</p>
          <p>An <a href="ch61s02.html#MonstersB-C16">abyssal greater basilisk's</a> natural weapons are treated as magic weapons for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.</p>
